      <div class="SOTTO_PARA"><a name="DUC0aa5ecd82b37100580ad8b55a208bfd2"></a>Removing the gearchange control
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6676"> </a>Loosen and remove the pin (1) securing the gearchange pedal (2), and recover the O-rings (3), the washer (4) and bush (5).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6678"> </a>Undo and remove the screw (6) securing the gearchange lever (7) to the gearbox shaft.
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6680"> </a>Withdraw the lever (7) complete with the gearchange control assembly.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_7_039603938.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_7_019803308.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_7_019903309.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="Attenzione"><img class="Attenzione" width="28" height="25" style="display: inline; float: none; left: 0.0; text-align: left; top: 0.0;" src="img/note.jpg">Note
      </div>
      <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6689"> </a>Mark the position of lever relative to the gear selector shaft.
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e6692"> </a>To remove lever (7) from gear transmission rod assembly (8), loosen screw (9) then slide out lever (7). 
         </div>
      </div>
